publicity.''
   He has been the subject of magazine article after magazine
article. They generally take one of two tacks, comparing him to
Ness, the crime-fighting hero of ``The Untouchables,'' or Girolamo
Savonarola, the 15th-century Italian monk and infamous zealot.
   If nothing else, Giuliani shares Savonarola's Catholicism. Born
in Brooklyn and raised on Long Island, he attended parochial schools
